# Stark profile correction tables for STARK_PROFILE (formerly SOFBET)
# S(beta,P) quasistatic ion microfield profiles for hydrogen lines
#
# Seven profile sets (INDX 1-7):
#   1: Lyman alpha  (N=1, M=2)
#   2: Lyman beta   (N=1, M=3)
#   3: Balmer alpha (N=2, M=3) = H-alpha
#   4: Balmer beta  (N=2, M=4) = H-beta
#   5: Paschen alpha(N=3, M=4)
#   6: Paschen beta (N=3, M=5)
#   7: Balmer 18    (N=2, M=18) -- generic high-n template
#
# PROPBM(5,15,7): correction table indexed by (P_index, beta_index, profile)
#   P_index 1-5: P = 0.0, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8
#   beta_index 1-15: beta = 1.0, 1.259, ..., 25.12 (log-spaced)
# C(5,7), D(5,7): asymptotic correction coefficients
#
